# ACL Rules for MQTT Security Auditor Testing

# Admin user can read and write to all topics, including system topics
user admin
topic readwrite #
topic readwrite $SYS/#

# Guest user has restricted access to guest/# topics only
user guest
topic readwrite guest/#

# Anonymous users (on port 1883) can read/write to factory/#
# but cannot write to other namespaces
pattern readwrite factory/#
